These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, animation, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | musical | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish, pony
1. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the pony##2
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Pet   | pony | rabbit | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
