1. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching western movies##2
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | crime | fantasy |

