2. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | card-games | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, techno, funk
